manifests.contents:
bin = []
bench = []
test = []

[[example]]
path = "examples/cli.rs"
name = "cli"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "movparse"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
async-trait = "0.1.59"

[dependencies.movparse-box]
path = "../movparse-box"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.movparse-derive]
path = "../movparse-derive"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.150"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.23.0"
features = ["io-util"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1.37"
features = []
optional = true

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.16"
features = ["env-filter"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.66"
serde_json = "1.0.89"

[dev-dependencies.clap]
version = "4.0.29"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[features]
tracing = ["dep:tracing", "movparse-box/tracing", "movparse-derive/tracing"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "movparse"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
